cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.CL

The paper deals with automatic signboard detection from natural scene images using image processing techniques and deep learning methods. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves information extraction from images, which falls under the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The use of deep learning methods suggests the possibility of sub-categories such as cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for text recognition, which could fall under the sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language).
